Option 1: stelfi is on CRAN

install.packages("stelfi")

Option 2: the development version of stelfi package can be installed from GitHub

devtools::install_github("cmjt/stelfi")
Note

To cite stelfi use

citation("stelfi")
To cite `stelfi` in pubications use:

  C. M. Jones-Todd, and A. B. M. van Helsdingen (2024), stelfi: An R
  package for fitting Hawkes and log-Gaussian Cox point process models,
  Ecology and Evolution, 14, e11005,doi:10.1002/ece3.11005

A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is
